BirthData.DetailedNotes: Conservationist. Painfully shy and fearful as a kid, learned to talk to animals. Outsider at the University, lost job for chronic lateness. Sense of language, avoids battles, natures true patroit. Autocratic, handsome, disquietingly intense, aimable zealot. Reserved, voice quiet and persuasively mellifluous. Engaging smile, lives in unpretentious house, zealous naturalist. CB 73.
